statistics:
    analytics: FPS, amount of Objects / vertecies currently loaded
    game: objects used, playtime, most used spell
    
    

gathering: current game, life time (player life), overall

display: on screen, in menu, where to find, in text file
        only for players or send to developers
        
During playtime the game will collect metrics like FPS, current loaded objects
and send them via HTTP to a server where they will be stored so developers can 
analyze them later.
